ILayerPanel, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
public class ArcImsWizard
extends WizardPanel

This class implements the wizard that enables the user to load an ArcIMS layer. Passes most requests on to its ArcImsWizardData dataSource object.

Author:
jldominguez

public void setEnabledPanels(java.lang.String selectedPanel)
Enables or disables the main panel and the layer selection panel.

Parameters:
selectedPanel - a String that identifies which panel must be enabled: "main" (for the service names panel) or "service" (for the layer selection panel).

fireWizardComplete

public void fireWizardComplete(boolean b)
Fires a notification to this wizard listeners telling them if the configuration is fair enough to send a GetMap request.

Parameters:
b - true if the data in the wizard is enough to send a getMap request and therefore create a new layer in the project; false otherwise.
